{
  "stem": "1775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 152.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, when you turned, one person turned, everybody had to turn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When one person sat up, everybody had to, you know, had to join in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Whatever anybody did, we all had to do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's how much space we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Afterwards, in-- during the evening, towards the evening, we used to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We used to gather food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We used to [? trap ?] [? stuff. ?] But mainly, I used to go and get the food, because nobody else was allowed to go with him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He didn't want nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I used to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was the only one to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "After-- after quite a while, and when the news was good, it was very good and generous to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was already January, February, and March.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then it started out, the partisans-- the Russians dropped partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when the [INAUDIBLE] would try to get a hold, and go connect with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we never could come together with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Whenever we-- we heard the rumor that they're here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And if we went there, [BACKROUND NOISE] they were gone, already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We always were a little too late.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we all stuck together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And at that particular time, they started being that the rails went through there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Every night, there was another explosion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The partisans used to dynamite the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So there were other explosions, and things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when spring came, the man insisted, we have to go away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were afraid the Germans were-- there was a lot of Germans nearby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were afraid they're going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They're going to burn them up in the houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "At that particular time, I don't remember how it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
